          <div class="d">ط§ظ„ط³ظ†ط© ط§ظ„ط£ظˆظ„ظ‰ ط§ظ„ظ…ط´طھط±ظƒط© <span class="sep">|</span> First-Year Common Program</div>
          <div class="s">3.3 ظ…ظ‚ط§ظٹظٹط³ ط§ظ„طھط´طھطھ <span class="sep">|</span> Dispersion Measures</div>
        </div>
      </div>
